Durban - The Colour of Magic came to life on Saturday  at the Vodacom Durban July 2017, as designers and guests portrayed their own interpretation of the theme.
 
Fashion on the Action Stage was one of the highlights of the event as designers, young and old, showcased their designs in between the first five races.
 
The designs were out of this world - Classic Racewear, Exceptional Raceday Hat or Fascinator, Huawei Most Striking Couple - left the crowd with dropped jaws.
 
Katekani Moreku, a young student from DUT, walked away with the Young Designer Award for a colourful piece worn by model, Luvuyo Shoba. To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
